Cheyra Bell (born 24 September 1988), is a Bermudian professional footballer who plays as a forward.
She studied at Howard University and is a sister of Tahj Bell, who played once for Bermuda.

response: His sister is Cheyra Bell, who plays for Bermuda women's national football team.People - Cheyra Bell - Royal Gazette His late father Derek was also a football player.
